State of Connecticut v. Kenneth Prutting (11998)

O’Connell, Lavery and Schaller, Js.

Argued February 8 decision released March 7, 1995 Dante R. Gallueci, special public defender, for the appellant (defendant). Richard F. Jacobson, assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, were Donald A. Browne, state’s attorney, and Stephen J. Sedensky, assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (state). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
